ygData.subject: Kill the Twinking Subject!!!
ygData.msgSnippet: My goodness i never thought that one message i sent to the guy telling em to leave twinking alone would turn into this, more than half my messages are about
ygData.messageBody:
My goodness i never thought that one message i sent to the guy telling em to
leave twinking alone would turn into this, more than half my messages are
about this same subject. Let's just leave it alone if you think it's wrong
then fine if you don't think it's wrong then your all ready leaving it
alone. Just play the game and have fun people. Don't make this a battle like
UO was. Can't we all just get along :)
